{"about_the_game":"Raven is a TPS Isometric 3D Roguelike Fight Game. Solve the Puzzles and Hunt the Goblins! Fight against Goblin King's Best Boss Fighters and Defeat the Goblin King to save your People from Slavery!<br><br>You have inventory. So you can collect useful items and tools. You can merge items and craft new weapons or make your existing weapons for powerful by upgrading them with extra tools. You have also a Spell Notebook. During your Journey, you will meet with different Wizards and learn new spells from them. You can check these spells from your Notebook whenever you want and use them against your Enemies!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427230/extras/9.gif?t=1687117347\" /><br><br>The Goblin King was making people work as slaves and ruthlessly using them to dig more tunnels under the ground, making more space for the king and the miserable goblin people to live in. Here our hero, Raven, was born in one of these slave villages, Acharaz.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427230/extras/8.gif?t=1687117347\" /><br><br>Raven, whose parents were killed by Goblin soldiers, swore to take revenge on the Goblin King one day. To escape this persecution, the Village's mage taught him the most powerful spells. The village blacksmith made the most dangerous and sharp weapons for him. And the chief, one of the old warriors of the village, taught him to fight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427230/extras/12.gif?t=1687117347\" /><br><br>Get ready to enter the dangerous Goblin Kingdom with Raven, hunt thousands of Goblins in desolate dungeons, solve puzzles and save your people from the Goblin King's tyranny! Adventure awaits you...","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1687117347",